321 Great Eastern Highway is strategically located on the upgraded Great Eastern Highway between Perth CBD and the Domestic Airport. This location has excellent access to Perth's road network, being close to Tonkin Highway and Graham Farmer Freeway.

The 320sqm* office/showroom space is open plan with one partitioned office and benefits from carpeted floors, suspended ceiling and air-conditioning. There is also two toilets and a kitchen.

The warehouse has a truss height of approximately 6.5m* and roller door access. There is parking at both the front and rear of the property. It measures 10.5m* wide by 30.5m* long.

*approx
